text: The Sweden women's national ice hockey team () represents the country of Sweden in women's ice hockey. The team started in 1987. It won bronze medals at the world championships in the years 2005 and 2007, Olympic bronze medal in 2002, and an Olympic silver medal in 2006. ==Other websites== Category:1987 establishments in Sweden Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:National ice hockey teams
